Haven't hosted an #artshare in a long time. So here it is!

🔹Share your art/projects & links! Support each other! 
🔹Repost this post to reach more people; 
🔹Keep it SFW please; 
🔹No AI/NFTs; 

I will repost the replies to this post throughout the day.

Let's do an Artshare!

- drop your art;
- like & rt;
- like and rt on other people works;
- tag your friends;
- follow each other (optional)
